Package com.gsm.dto

Class OrderBOMDetailDto

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gsm.dto.OrderBOMDetailDto
  • public class OrderBOMDetailDto
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a single line item within an Order BOM, corresponding to one material. This DTO is used to transfer data between the view and the controller for Order BOM details.
